						<div class="postbody">I dunno what you're doing, but if you're doing something with a sub-pixel or decimal to get a fine tune on things, just use a low byte that only changes the high byte when it &quot;rolls over&quot; so that way you can add stuff each from but nothing happens.</div>

					
